ent-BodyBag = body bag
    .desc = A plastic bag designed for the storage and transportation of cadavers. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
ent-BodyBagFolded = body bag
    .desc = A plastic bag designed for the storage and transportation of cadavers. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
