ent-BodyBagEnvironmental = environmental protection bag
    .desc = An insulated, reinforced bag designed to protect against exoplanetary storms and other environmental factors. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
ent-BodyBagEnvironmentalFolded = environmental protection bag
    .desc = An insulated, reinforced bag designed to protect against exoplanetary storms and other environmental factors. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
