ent-BodyBagPrisoner = prisoner transport bag
    .desc = Intended for transport of prisoners through hazardous environments, this environmental protection bag comes with straps to keep an occupant secure. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
ent-BodyBagPrisonerFolded = prisoner transport bag
    .desc = Intended for transport of prisoners through hazardous environments, this environmental protection bag comes with straps to keep an occupant secure. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
    .suffix = folded
ent-BodyBagSyndicate = syndicate prisoner transport bag
    .desc = An alteration of Nanotrasen's environmental protection bag which has been used in several high-profile kidnappings. Designed to keep a victim secure during transport. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
ent-BodyBagSyndicateFolded = syndicate prisoner transport bag
    .desc = An alteration of Nanotrasen's environmental protection bag which has been used in several high-profile kidnappings. Designed to keep a victim secure during transport. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
    .suffix = folded
ent-BodyBagStasis = stasis body bag
    .desc = A disposable bodybag designed to keep its contents in stasis, completely stopping decay and preventing further injury. The bag itself cannot maintain stasis for long, and will eventually fall apart.
ent-BodyBagStasisFolded = stasis body bag
    .desc = A disposable bodybag designed to keep its contents in stasis, preventing decay and further injury.
    .suffix = folded
ent-BodyBagLostCrew = long-term body bag
    .desc = A plastic bag designed for the long-term storage and transportation of cadavers. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
ent-BodyBagLostCrewFolded = long-term body bag
    .desc = A plastic bag designed for the long-term storage and transportation of cadavers. Slows bodily decomposition by two thirds.
    .suffix = folded
ent-BodyBagLostCrewWithBody = long-term body bag
    .desc = A plastic bag containing the remains of a lost crew member.
